articles.title: Jordan's Visual Analytics Site
articles.description: Welcome to the website! Hope you will enjoy the visuals I created!
articles.contents:
This website is a collection of all the exercises and assignments
that are required under ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications.
If you have any feedback or need any clarification, you may contact
Jordan at jordan.ong.2021@mitb.smu.edu.sg.
I hope you enjoy the website. Stay Safe!
